<section class="cc-what">
  <div class="cc-what__inner">
    <div class="cc-what__text">
      <span class="cc-what__label">What is CØRT Club</span>
      <h2 class="cc-what__heading">Padel deserves a proper community.</h2>
      <p class="cc-what__body">The UK padel scene is exploding — but it's scattered. Courts are popping up everywhere, players are hungry to compete, and clubs are running events with no way to connect them. CØRT Club fixes that.</p>
      <p class="cc-what__body">We're building the grassroots infrastructure that padel never had: structured local events, player connections, and a ratings system that actually means something.</p>
      <a href="#join" class="cc-btn-primary" style="margin-top:8px;">Get Early Access</a>
    </div>
    <div class="cc-what__visual">
      <div class="cc-what__point">
        <div class="cc-what__point-icon">1</div>
        <div class="cc-what__point-text">
          <div class="cc-what__point-title">Find local events</div>
          Americanos, league nights, socials — all in one feed near you.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="cc-what__point">
        <div class="cc-what__point-icon">2</div>
        <div class="cc-what__point-text">
          <div class="cc-what__point-title">Connect with players</div>
          Find partners at your level. No more WhatsApp groups going cold.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="cc-what__point">
        <div class="cc-what__point-icon">3</div>
        <div class="cc-what__point-text">
          <div class="cc-what__point-title">Build your rating</div>
          Every match counts. Your CØRT Rating follows you across every event.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="cc-what__point">
        <div class="cc-what__point-icon">4</div>
        <div class="cc-what__point-text">
          <div class="cc-what__point-title">Compete for real</div>
          Sponsor-backed tournaments with proper prizes — not just a trophy.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

